The Enterprise receives an old style SOS signal and finds on arrival a planet that
is virtually identical to Earth. Kirk, Spock, McCoy and Yeoman Rand beam down to
the planet only to find that it is inhabited solely by children. Kirk befriends one of

all of the adults and that the children will also die when they reach puberty. They
also learn that the children are in fact, very old. Soon, the landing party contracts
the virus and they have seven days to find a cure.
